        </ul>

        <h2>Your Next Step</h2>

        <p>If you're considering remodeling your kitchen, the first step is a free in-home consultation. No commitment, no sales pressure. We simply listen to your needs, analyze the space, and explain the possibilities.</p>

        <p>During the visit:</p>

        <ul>
          <li>We take precise measurements</li>
          <li>We analyze your daily kitchen routine</li>
          <li>We identify current problems and improvement opportunities</li>
          <li>We show you examples of similar projects</li>
          <li>We answer all your questions</li>
          <li>We give you an indicative budget range</li>
        </ul>

        <p>If you decide to move forward, within a few days you'll have a complete design with 3D renders and detailed quote. If not, at least you'll have professional ideas to consider.</p>

        <p><strong>Ready to transform your kitchen?</strong> <a href="/en/contact">Schedule your free consultation</a> today and take the first step toward the kitchen you've always dreamed of.</p>
      </div>
